title: Platinum & Diamond Support Players Wanted
body:
Howdy I'm Tedd, a Plat 1 AD main (https://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=Tedd)

I'm currently sitting in my Diamond promotion games looking for some high calibre support action to grind out some games with either helping you climb to Diamond or past Diamond 4.

If you average B+ support games and have win rates above 55% add me in game (:
